com.vector.cfg.gen.core.bswmdmodel

Interface GIModelAccess

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IGeneratorModelAccess

    @NotThreadSafe
 @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
public interface GIModelAccess
    This interface defines the available model access services for the bswmd model.

      • getGenModelObjectByMDFObject

        @PublishedMethod
GIModelObject getGenModelObjectByMDFObject(com.vector.cfg.model.mdf.model.autosar.ecucdescription.MIHasDefinition mdfCfgElement)
        Gets the corresponding BswmdModel GIModelObject by an MDF configuration element, or creates the BswmdModel GIModelObject, if it does not exist.
        Parameters:
        mdfCfgElement - the MDF element to wrap in a GIModelObject.
        Returns:
        The corresponding bswmd model object of the passed element.

      • getGenModelObjectByMDFObject

        @PublishedMethod
GIModelObject getGenModelObjectByMDFObject(com.vector.cfg.model.mdf.model.autosar.ecucdescription.MIHasDefinition mdfCfgElement,
                                                             DefRef defRef)
        Gets the corresponding BswmdModel GIModelObject by an MDF configuration element, or creates the BswmdModel GIModelObject, if it does not exist.
        Parameters:
        mdfCfgElement - the MDF element to wrap in a GIModelObject.
        defRef - The DefRef of the passed element.
        Returns:
        The corresponding bswmd model object of the passed element.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException -
        • if the mdfCfgElement is not an instance of the passed defRef.
        • if the mdfCfgElement is null.
        • if the defRef is null.
